A 46 Year Old Man Has Been Arrested For Allegedly Defiling A One And A Half Year Old Baby In Bulapesa Area Of Isiolo County. According To Isiolo Sub County Police Commander Moses Owiti, The Child Was Defiled By The Suspect In One Of The Rooms In The Neighbourhoods Of Their Home. Owiti Says That That The Suspect Who Is A Relative To The Minor Picked The Child From Their Home And Took Her To A Room Where She Was Defiled. TheÂ Mother Of The Child Had Left Her Lying On The Bed As She Went To A Nearby Shop. The Baby Was Taken To Isiolo Referral Hospital Where Medics Confirmed That Indeed The Girl Had Been Defiled Causing Her To Bleed From Her Genitalia. The Suspect Is Expected To Be Arraigned In Court.